trans-unit.source: The ServiceNameElement class represents a configuration element for a service name used in a <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: ServiceNameElement 類別表示組態項目中使用服務名稱<xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: When this constructor is used to initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> class, the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: 當這個建構函式用來初始化的新執行個體<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>類別<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>屬性設定為`null`。</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A> property should be set to an appropriate value for the application before calling the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A> method to add the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement> instance to the <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>屬性應該設定為適當的值，然後再呼叫<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>方法，將<xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement><xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>類別</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection>的執行個體</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement></xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElementCollection.Add%2A>的應用程式</xref:System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Service Provider Name (SPN) for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定這個服務提供者名稱 (SPN) <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"> </xref>執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the representation of SPN for this <xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.String>其中包含表示法的 SPN，這個<xref href="System.Security.Authentication.ExtendedProtection.Configuration.ServiceNameElement"></xref>執行個體。</xref:System.String>
